c_t
H_t = e^{-\rho t}\ln(c_t) + \lambda_t (f(k_t)-c_t)
\frac{\partial H}{\partial c_t} = 0 
\frac{\partial H}{\partial k_t} = -\dot{\lambda}_t
lim_{t \rightarrow \infty} \lambda_t k_t =0
\dot{\lambda}_t = -\lambda_t (\rho + \frac{\dot{c}_t}{c_t})
c_t
